Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.44,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,By the decision of Ying Zheng, the king that wished to unite all of China,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:09.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N天下統一の道を行く王 嬴政(えいせい)のもと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.19,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the State of Qin began its invasion of the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国(しんこく)は 魏国(ぎこく)へと侵攻した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:16.57,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The enemy blocking their way is the legendary Great General, Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:16.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ちはだかる敵は\N伝説の大将軍 廉頗(れんぱ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:22.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若き将たちは 大いなる武功を狙い\Nこの苛烈な戦場に挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:22.87,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Young generals take on this relentless battlefield in hopes of rendering great military achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:26.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎(かんき)）\N言い残すことはあるか？ じいさん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.37,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Any last words, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:28.36,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,You may be ignorant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:30.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰(げんぽう)）ものを知らぬが\N確かに筋は悪くない …か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:30.92,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,but you certainly have talent, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:35.01,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind taking you on as a disciple, Huan Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弟子にしてやってもよいぞ 桓騎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N要るかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.38,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Like I want your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.19,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雑魚が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.76,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Xuan Feng. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）許せ 玄峰…\Nつまらぬ死に方をさせた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.79,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,I let you die a boring death... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.11,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,I can't say anything too soft while I'm on the battlefield, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場で生ぬるいことは言えぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:52.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけ共に\N死線を越えてきた うぬを失うとは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:52.46,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,but losing you after we faced death together so many times is... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:56.53,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,But there's no reason to feel lonely, Xuan Feng. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 寂しがることはないぞ 玄峰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:02.78,Kingdom-Thought,Huan,0,0,0,,Soon that side will be flooded with the corpses of State of Qin soldiers! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:01:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに 秦国兵の骸(むくろ)で\Nそっちをあふれ返してやるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）やったぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Huan Ji's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（慶(けい)）桓騎将軍 すげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂(こう)）おいらたち中央軍の敵(かたき)を\N取ってくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:19.19,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,He got revenge for us, the central army!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:20.83,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:20.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）良かった！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:23.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのじじい また妙な術を\N仕掛けてくるんじゃねえかって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.02,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Even I was afraid that old man would be coming at us with another weird strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがの俺もビクついてたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:28.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永(でんえい)）\N尾平のビビリは いつもじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:28.61,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Wei Ping, you're {/i1}always{/i0} afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）アハッ… アハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:38.65,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Xuan Feng...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:38.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信(しん)）玄峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）信じられねえ　あのじじいが\Nあっさり やられるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:44.70,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I can't believe it... That old man got done in that easily? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Meng Tian?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いねえのか？ 蒙恬(もうてん)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.42,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:53.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）ああ\N桓騎将軍自ら伝令兵に変装して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:55.45,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Apparently General Huan Ji personally disguised himself as a messenger soldier and snuck into the enemy headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:57.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の本陣に忍び込んだらしい\N（信）なに？ もっと詳しく教えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:56.18,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:57.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Could you be a little more detailed about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…と その前に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:59.72,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well, before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:02.39,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I've got somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行く所があるんだ\Nお前も一緒に来い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.68,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ… 行く所？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.35,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Somewhere to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:11.73,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.25\c&H000000&\pos(638,101.667)}Meng Tian's Proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（武将）輪虎(りんこ)将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:31.68,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,General Lun Hu, I understand how you feel, but we really must begin the war council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お気持ちは分かりますが\N軍議を開いてください
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:37.88,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Due to the errors in the left army, everyone is clamoring about what strategy we should take as the central army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左軍の失態により 我ら中央軍の\N作戦は どうなるのかと―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆が騒いでおります
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:43.57,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Could you please—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか…\N（輪虎）うるさいなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:44.64,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Man, you're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.53,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I lost my parents in a war
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）僕は 戦で両親を失い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.65,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,and I was saved by my lord when I was at the verge of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飢え死にしそうなところを\N殿に助けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:05.41,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Since then, I've devoted everything to become my lord's sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それからの僕は―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:05.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿の剣となるために\N全てをささげたわけだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:10.19,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,but it was actually Lord Xuan Feng that taught me strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:09.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）実際に戦術なんかを\N教えてくれたのは 玄峰さまだった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:21.46,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,It's always felt to me that my lord is my father and that man is my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕にとって\N殿が父なら あの人は祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.18,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I had a great debt with the second of those two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２番目に\N恩を返さなきゃいけない人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:44.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに 討たれたからには\Nヘマをした玄峰さまが悪いんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.98,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Of course, seeing as he was the one beaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.82,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Lord Xuan Feng is the one at fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:50.61,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,but if you say something like "I understand how you feel" so casually
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“気持ちは分かる”なんて\N軽々しく言われると―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:52.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 イラッと来るな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.20,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I honestly get pretty annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:57.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い… いえ… それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.65,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）心配いらない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:05.22,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,After tonight, my lord will have cemented a whole new strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜 ひと晩で\N殿は新しい戦略を固められる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.66,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Then the only thing left will be to follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは それに従うだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:33.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Why the hell did I hafta come to a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで俺が こんなとこに\N来なきゃなんねえんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:36.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言うなって\N大事な話があるんだからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:37.12,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be like that. I've got something really important to tell you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:42.63,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And aren't you worried, seeing what bad shape the Yufeng Unit is in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:42.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに このところの玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊の\N調子の悪さを見ると 心配だろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:46.73,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Or about that guy's wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつのケガの具合も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜ… 全然！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I ain't friggin' worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お見舞いに来たよ 王賁(おうほん)　入るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.98,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,We're here to visit you on your sickbed, Wang Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.64,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,We're coming in now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）アア…\N（蒙恬）あら 元気そう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.64,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Ah, he looks pretty healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.15,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）何の用だ？\N（蒙恬）ハハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:07.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ya see! There's no point in worryin' about this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほらな！ こんなヤツ\N心配するだけ損なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.53,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,You're in the way. Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャマだ　出ていけ\N（信）言われなくたって出ていくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell me twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.39,Kingdom-Main,Men,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:17.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）まあまあ…\N王賁も 信も 座って座って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.69,Kingdom-Main,Men,0,0,0,,C'mon, Wang Ben, Xin, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信･王賁）お前が仕切るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.76,Kingdom-Main,Both,0,0,0,,Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:29.36,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,You've heard about how Xuan Feng was slain, Wang Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\N桓騎将軍が玄峰を討ったこと\N王賁も聞いたよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.48,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）ああ\N（蒙恬）驚いたろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.55,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.49,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に\N（信）ウソつけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:41.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ… お前たち２人が手も足も\N出なかった玄峰を瞬殺だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:41.56,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well you two couldn't lay a finger on that guy, and then he got killed instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:46.57,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If I'd aimed by spear just a little better, I would've taken that old man out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の槍(やり)は もうちょっとで\Nあのじじいに届くとこだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフッ… 俺は驚いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.29,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:54.33,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I'd heard that General Huan Ji was a military genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎将軍は戦の天才だと\N聞いていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:58.08,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,but I honestly didn't think he'd be able to pull off something this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 ここまで大仕事を\Nやってのけるとは思っていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:04.21,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,So I'm saying that as people aiming for the top, we have some huge walls right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上を目指す俺たちの すぐ上には\Nでっかい壁があるって話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:11.81,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Including how to overcome those walls, we need to think about what we're going to do from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その壁を越えるためにも―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからのことを\N考えておかないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:26.61,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,This is the headquarters where the State of Qin Army Supreme Commander, General Meng Ao, is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが 秦国軍の\N総大将 蒙驁(もうごう)将軍がいる本陣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その前方に 俺たちの\N組み込まれている中央軍が布陣し…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.91,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,The army we're a part of, the central army, will be in formation just in front of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.42,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,To our right will be the right army, led by General Huan Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:34.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの右には\N桓騎将軍率いる右軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:39.52,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And on the left, the left army led by Wang Jian will be developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左には 王翦(おうせん)将軍率いる左軍が\N展開している
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:44.96,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,On the other side of things, the State of Wei headquarters will be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:44.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一方 敵 魏国軍の本陣は この辺り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに敵の総大将 白亀西と…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.73,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,This is where the enemy Supreme Commander, Bai Guixi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.25,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,and most likely, Lian Po, will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく 今のところは廉頗がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:07:00.75,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,In front of the enemy headquarters will be the army directly in front of us, the enemy central army led by Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の本陣の前方\N俺たちの正面に―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:00.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎の率いる\N敵の中央軍がいて…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.14,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And I would expect armies on the left and right will be developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 右と左にも\N軍が展開している
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前置きが長いぞ\Nさっさと本題に入れ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.18,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,That's enough of a preface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.90,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Get to the point already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フゥ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）玄峰を討ったあと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:16.41,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,After slaying Xuan Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.81,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,General Huan Ji and his subordinates disappeared altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎将軍は\N配下の兵もろとも姿を消した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一気に\N敵の本陣を狙うのでは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:25.73,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,One could make the assumption they would head straight for the enemy headquarters, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…という推測もあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:29.94,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,they actually drew back, rushing to regroup their army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は 後方に下がって\N軍の立て直しを急いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立て直し？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Regroup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:35.44,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yes. Xuan Feng made light of Huan Ji,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　玄峰は桓騎を侮ったが\N桓騎も介子坊(かいしぼう)を侮った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.55,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,but Huan Ji also made light of Jie Zifang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:42.47,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,General Huan Ji's headquarters was attacked by Jie Zifang's army
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:42.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）桓騎将軍の本陣は\N介子坊の軍の襲撃を受け―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵士の半数を失ったそうだ\N（信）介子坊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.80,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,and it seems he lost half of his soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Jie Zifang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:50.02,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,The general leading the enemy left army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の左軍を率いている将軍だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:55.17,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,But having lost track of Huan Ji, Jie Zifang has to always be on his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ 桓騎を見失った介子坊も\Nうかつには動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.20,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And on the opposite side of the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一方 戦場の反対側では―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:02.91,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,it seems that the one leading the enemy right army, Jiang Yan, has moved in to attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の右軍を率いる姜燕(きょうえん)が\N攻め込んできたようだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:07.21,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,but I don't see it as possible that General Wang Jian will simply be overcome by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王翦将軍が そのまま\N押し切られるなんて ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.08,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Don't you think, Wang Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろう？ 王賁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:15.33,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,In other words, both the right army and left army are at a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり\N右の軍も左の軍も膠着(こうちゃく)状態で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくは\N戦況が動きそうもないってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:19.15,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,So it doesn't look like the state of battle will be changing for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右や左の話は\Nそれくらいでいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.58,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Well that's fine for the left and right armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:25.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But the one we're fighting is Lun Hu, right in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが戦ってるのは\N真ん中の輪虎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.56,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,You really don't understand anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も分かってないな お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.36,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信の言葉は\N半分 合ってて 半分 間違ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.87,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well Xin, what you said was half right and half wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:41.83,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,It's true that our problem lies with Lun Hu in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに 俺たちにとって問題なのは\N中央の輪虎なんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その輪虎の動きが\N左右の軍の動きと―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.67,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,but Lun Hu's movements will be connected with the movements of the left and right armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,密接に関係してるんだ\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.12,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,In these three days
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）\Nこの３日間 中央の輪虎軍は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:55.47,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,the Lun Hu Army in the center has been waiting to decide whether to push into their opponents on the right or the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右か左の軍が\N相手を押し込むのを待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気を出していない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.09,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,so they haven't been serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:03.05,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,The reason we didn't have major casualties on the second day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２日目以降 こちらに\N大した被害が出ていないのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守備に徹しているせいもあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:05.40,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,was because they were focusing on defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:12.97,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,We'd be correct in thinking that Lun Hu, one of Lian Po's Four Heavenly Kings, was not acting in all seriousness then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:12.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗四天王のひとり 輪虎が 本気を\N出していないと考えるほうが妥当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:17.01,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Hey, did you do some investigating on Lun Hu, Wang Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとして\N輪虎のこと調べた？ 王賁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:22.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多少　部下に敵の捕虜を当たらせた\N（蒙恬）なるほど… さすがだね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:20.59,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,A little. I had my subordinates get it from enemy prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.83,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,I see. Good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:27.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ちょ… ちょっと待て！\Nズルイぞ お前ら　俺にも教えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.07,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That ain't fair, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Tell me this stuff, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:32.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗の下には\N四天王と呼ばれる４人の将軍がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:32.77,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Lian Po has four generals under him called the Four Heavenly Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:38.70,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,They're all genuinely strong people that have built up military experience fighting with Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いずれも\N廉頗と共に戦歴を重ねてきた―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,極めつきの つわものたちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.66,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,The head of the Four Heavenly Kings, Jie Zifang,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）四天王筆頭の介子坊は\N廉頗と関わりなく―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.87,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,is a military hero that has had victory in over 100 wars even without Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単独でも 100を超える戦で\N勝利を収めてきた豪傑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.69,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,The expert bowman and one of China's Ten Bows, Jiang Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華十弓のひとりに\N数えられる弓の名手 姜燕は―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて\N趙国(ちょうこく)と対立していた国の英雄だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.17,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,was once a hero of a kingdom that once opposed the State of Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:02.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さんざん\N廉頗を手こずらせたというが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:02.52,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,They apparently caused a lot of trouble for Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:05.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国が滅んだあとは\N廉頗に忠誠を誓っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.70,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,but after their kingdoms crumbled, they swore loyalty to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.87,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xuan Feng, a long-time officer under Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\N長年 廉頗の参謀を務めた玄峰は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙国軍全体の総司令を\N任されるほどの実力を―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:15.06,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,apparently was skilled enough to command the entire State of Zhao Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っていたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That old man... He was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのじじい そんなに偉かったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:25.36,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,By the way, Xuan Feng also taught Lian Po war strategy in his younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちなみに 玄峰は 若き日の廉頗に\N戦略を教えた師でもあった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その玄峰を弔うためにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:27.68,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,And it's likely that as a way of mourning Xuan Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.31,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Lian Po will do everything he can to win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は全力で\Nこの戦を勝ちに来るだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:40.32,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And the last one, the one we're opposing now, Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 最後のひとり…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 俺たちが\N相手にしている輪虎だが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗の戦歴を詳しく知ったら\N分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.07,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,From all I learned from Lian Po's war history, this is what became apparent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:49.75,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,the most dangerous one among the Four Heavenly Kings is indeed Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）やはり 四天王の中で\N最も危険なのは この輪虎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗が関わった大きな戦では―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.45,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,In all of the big wars Lian Po was involved in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず この男が\N決定的な戦果を挙げている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.99,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,that man always made decisive military gains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく\N恐ろしい突破力を持っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.40,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He also boasts incredible ability to break through opposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎に本陣を襲われた軍は\N数知れない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.34,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Lun Hu has attacked countless enemy headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:05.15,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He's even penetrated General Wang Qi's headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王騎(おうき)将軍も 本陣に突入され
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎に ひと太刀浴びせられている\N（信）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:07.30,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,and struck a blow on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:07.85,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:13.74,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,He struck a blow... on Wang Qi?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王騎将軍に…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひと太刀 浴びせた？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:21.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So that Lun Hu hasn't shown his true colors yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:22.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ本気出してねえな 輪虎は\N（蒙恬）全然ね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.68,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Not in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:27.86,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,If the enemy left army or right army gets behind General Meng Ao, blocking his escape route,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）敵の右軍か左軍が―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁将軍の後ろに回り\N逃げ道を塞げば―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.56,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Lun Hu could push in for an attack on a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎は\Nすかさず攻め込んでくるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:35.76,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Do you think that we, the central army, could stop Lun Hu when he's attacking seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で攻めてくる輪虎を―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:35.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち中央軍で\N止められると思うかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）はっきり言って ムリだな\N（信）なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.97,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ そうだよね\N（信）ちょっと待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.36,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.01,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're you guys talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:49.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ お前ら！\N戦う前から諦めてんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.18,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We can't give up before we've even fought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎が玄峰を討ったんなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Huan Ji took down Xuan Feng, so how can we say we're aiming even higher
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その上を目指す俺たちが\N輪虎を討たなくて どうするんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.89,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,if we can't take out Lun Hu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:12:00.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This is the guy that struck a blow on General Wang Qi! I say, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:12:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N王騎将軍に ひと太刀浴びせた輪虎\N上等じゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来るなら来いってんだ！\N返り討ちにしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let him come at us if he wants, we'll hit him right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.64,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケッ… ちょうどいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:10.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm the one who first formed a connection to that guy, and my goal is the head of one general!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつと\N最初に因縁ができたのは俺だし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目的の“将軍の首１つ”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:16.63,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll take the head of one of Lian Po's Four Heavenly Kings with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:16.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗四天王のひとり 輪虎の首は\N必ず俺が この手で取ってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:20.29,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And then I'll move ahead of you two in one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 一気に\Nお前らの上に行ってやっからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほえるだけなら誰でもできる\N身の程知らずが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.41,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Anyone can talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.67,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,You idiot, you don't know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:33.43,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xin, you're half right, half wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信… 今度も\N半分 合ってて 半分 間違い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:39.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じいさまの本陣を狙っている輪虎は\N確かに討ち取らなくっちゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:39.13,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,It's true that since Lun Hu is targeting Grandfather's headquarters, we need to take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 攻め込んでくるのを\N返り討ちにするんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.64,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,But we can't do that by countering when he attacks us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.15,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Meng Tian, what exactly are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬… 貴様 何が言いたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:51.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻めてくる輪虎を\N止めるのがムリなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:51.75,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,If stopping Lun Hu once he starts his attack is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.26,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,then we just don't let him attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻めさせなきゃいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:59.62,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,In other words, we wage an attack and defeat Lun Hu before he has a chance to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:59.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 輪虎が攻めてくる前に\Nこちらから仕掛けて 倒すのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:07.74,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we have the Yuehua Unit, the Yufeng Unit, and the Feixin Unit attack in a group
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日 楽華(がくか)隊 玉鳳隊 飛信(ひしん)隊の\N３隊で打って出て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.13,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,and take down Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を討ち取ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.81,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs50\be0.5\pos(292,102.267)}Meng Tian
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.14,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yuehua Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この隊の長所は\N緻密で冷静な戦い方と―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:55.60,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,This unit's forte is that we can perform in a meticulous and level-headed fighting style,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泥くさい血みどろの戦い方\N両方ができることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.77,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,as well as an unrefined, bloody fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.60,Kingdom-Thought,Gramps,0,0,0,,The young master is giving a pep-talk? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（じい）若が 檄(げき)を…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.60,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,That's rare... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陸仙(りくせん)）珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.61,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And today, we will be doing the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）そして 今日は後者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.76,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,As you know, I'm really not a fan of this sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってのとおり\Nこういうノリは好きじゃないが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:15.12,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,but right now there's something before us that only we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちにしかできないことが\N今 目の前にある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.87,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Today's going to be a brutal life-or-death struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は ひどい死闘になるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.75,Kingdom-Thought,Gramps,0,0,0,,I see. So that's what's going on? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど… そういうことでしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:29.26,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,He's intending to do an important job for the first time in a while. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,久々に\N重要な役目を果たすおつもりですな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いが よろしく頼むよ みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.51,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm really gonna be counting on you guys for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.24,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）何だ？ 楽華隊の連中が\Nやけに張り切っているが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.15,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Those Yuehua guys sound really spirited about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:59.18,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,The Yuehue Unit seems to be in a different mood than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水(そすい)）楽華隊の様子が\Nいつもと違いますな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.29,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Chu Shui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楚水\N（楚水）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.92,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I've got something I need to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ちょっと話がある
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）輪虎将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A message from the main headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）総本陣より 伝令です！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.81,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,The battle will flow to the end of today. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“戦いは今日まで流す”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:28.75,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,So the battle for avenging Lord Xuan Feng will start tomorrow? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄峰さまの弔い合戦は明日以降か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.07,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Okay, how 'bout we get going then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！ それじゃ 始めようか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:46.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土門(どもん)）うろたえるな！\N守備に徹すれば 問題はない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.44,Kingdom-Main,Yu,0,0,0,,Do not panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.83,Kingdom-Main,Yu,0,0,0,,As long as you focus on defense, there will be no problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.02,Kingdom-Main,Yu,0,0,0,,Keep your heads level and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:52.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土門）落ち着いて戦え！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.80,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Tu Men! We have a situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下）土門将軍 大変です！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命令を無視して\N突撃していく部隊があります！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:58.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There is a unit that is ignoring orders and charging!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土門）なに！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.35,Kingdom-Main,Yu,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.35,Kingdom-Main,Yu,0,0,0,,The Yuehua Unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊か！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.17,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Tu Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）土門将軍！\N楽華隊の蒙恬千人将より伝達です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I have a message from Thousand-Man General Meng Tian of the Yuehua Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Yuehua Unit will now be acting as an independent army
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“楽華隊は\Nこれより独立軍となり―”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:14.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“兵200を残して\N持ち場を離れる”とのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,and will be leaving their post, leaving 200 soldiers behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.86,Kingdom-Main,Tu,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They've made killing them easier by saving us a trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）わざわざ\N討たれに出てくるとは手間が省ける
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り囲んで しとめろ！\N（魏兵たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.92,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Surround them and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.65,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yuehua Unit, progress to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊！ 右に進め！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.49,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,So that's Lun Hu's headquarters? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが輪虎の本陣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:03.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Lun Hu, there is one enemy unit that is charging straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭）輪虎さま 敵軍の中に―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっすぐ こちらに\N突っ込んでくる部隊があります
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:09.58,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Oh? I wonder if it's me they're aiming for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワハッ…\N狙いは ここにいる僕かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:13.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍の作戦ではなさそうだけど\N単独だとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.46,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like a strategy the State of Qin Army would use,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.88,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,so if someone's acting on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで自殺行為だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.88,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That's pretty much suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:35.11,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,After we've been competing with each other all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）これまで何かと\N張り合ってきた俺たち３人が―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手を組むのが難しいことぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.52,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,I know the three of us teaming up will be pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.71,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,But unless we try, we'll just all go down together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも このままじゃ 共倒れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:45.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,As we are now, the Yuehua Unit can't beat Lun Hu alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:45.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の楽華隊じゃ\N単独で輪虎を討つことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは玉鳳隊も飛信隊も同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,The same goes for the Yufeng Unit and Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.10,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, don't go grouping the Feixin Unit in with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手に飛信隊を一緒にすんな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:56.98,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Although you've gotten by through being stubborn like this up till now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:56.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までなら こうやって 意地を\N張り合っていても良かったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.47,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,the situation has majorly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,状況が大きく変わってきた\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:04.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに至るまで ３つの城を落とし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.99,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Until we got here, we took down three castles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉鳳隊 楽華隊 飛信隊と\Nそれぞれ武功を上げてきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:09.27,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,and the Yufeng Unit, Yuehua Unit, and Feixin Unit rendered our own individual achievements,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:16.08,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,but to be perfectly honest, those achievements didn't even resonate within the State of Qin, let alone other kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\Nはっきり言って そんな武功など
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの国はおろか\N秦国の国内にすら鳴り響いていない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:17.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:22.24,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,But now, we're fighting {\i1}the{\i0} Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:22.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは今 あの廉頗と戦っている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:27.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝説の大将軍 廉頗が\N参戦してきたことで―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:27.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Since the legendary Great General, Lian Po, is part of this war,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この山陽(さんよう)攻略の最終戦は―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:33.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,all of China will have its eyes on this final battle for the capture of Shanyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:33.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華全土が注目するものに\Nなったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 中華全土が注目…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.63,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of China?{\i0} {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:43.74,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,But as things stand, we cannot defeat Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）だが 今のままでは\N輪虎を討つことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を討てなければ―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:48.99,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,And unless we do, our Supreme Commander, General Meng Ao, will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらの総大将 蒙驁将軍の\N首が危ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし蒙驁将軍が\N討たれるようなことがあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.17,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,If something like General Meng Ao being killed happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.67,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,it won't be like the State of Zhao Army where they were trained and led by their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:56.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自らの手で鍛え上げ\N自在に操れる趙国軍ではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よそ者として指揮をする魏国軍を\N率いた廉頗に―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:19:02.53,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,we would be defeated by the State of Wei Army led by Lian Po, and outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは敗れたことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:06.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Then how the hell could we ever call ourselves the greatest generals under the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“天下の大将軍”などと\Nどの口がたたく？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:19.17,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to hear the words "greatest generals under the heavens" from you, Meng Tian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:19.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の口から“天下の大将軍”と\Nいう言葉が出るとはな 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:21.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.73,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その辺に関しては―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は お前たちほど\N熱いものは抱えちゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:28.02,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,I'm not as enthused about that as you two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:33.85,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,But for this time, I'm a bit different\N than I usually am, Wang Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 今回ばかりは\Nいつもの俺とは違うんだよ 王賁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:36.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？\N（蒙恬）さっきも言ったが―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,I said this earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.07,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,but we can't let them take Meng Ao's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁の首を\N取られるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:49.07,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Because he's my dear Grandfather that's always looking after this wandering, carefree grandson of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フラフラ遊び回っている\N俺みたいな孫を―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも見守ってくれている―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の大切なじいさまだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 自分１人の感情を\N戦場に持ち込むなど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:20:00.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,You're bringing personal feelings onto the battlefield? Ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くだらん\N（信）くだらなくはねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:02.11,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,It ain't ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Everybody fights for the things that are important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:07.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だって 自分の大事なもんや―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:10.85,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,For the things they can't let go of!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:10.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,譲れねえもんを守るために\N戦ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.35,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, Meng Tian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:22.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）いいぜ 蒙恬\N飛信隊は お前に乗っかってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit is on board with your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,It's about time we took the leading role in a war
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ戦の主役が変わるって―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華全土に\N教えてやらねえといけねえしな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.45,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,and told all of China who we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,So, what're you gonna do, Wang Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…で お前は どうする？ 王賁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Ben,0,0,0,,It depends on your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作戦しだいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.33,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll tell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）じゃ 作戦を言おう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:46.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,First, the Yuehua Unit will target Lun Hu's headquarters on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは\N楽華隊が単独で輪虎の本陣を目指す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:50.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど　錐行(すいこう)の陣か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.72,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.20,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,A pyramid formation, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その数で僕を狙うなら\N一点突破しかないからねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:55.35,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,If they're going for me with those numbers, their only chance is breaking through at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:21:00.35,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Let's see it then, the State of Qin Army's penetrative power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:21:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せてもらおうか　秦国軍の突破力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:06.36,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Hold on a second. Then that means you're just going to take down Lun Hu yourself, doesn't it?! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ちょっと待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ 結局 お前らだけで\N輪虎を倒しに行くんじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）\Nハハッ… それができないから\N策を講じてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:11.36,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,We're working out this plan because I can't do that, aren't we? {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.37,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Here we go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるぞ みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:21.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're trying to break through at one point! Defensive unit, take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一点突破 来るぞ！ 守備隊 構え！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:26.88,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:30.38,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:35.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,For the first stage of the plan... {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）作戦の第１段階
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華隊は輪虎を狙わない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.67,Kingdom-Flashback,Tian,0,0,0,,the Yuehua Unit will not target Lun Hu. {Flashback}
